464
00:40:49,375 --> 00:40:51,467
Daću sve od sebe da vam pronaðem...
- Hektore!

465
00:40:51,667 --> 00:40:54,092
Nisam mogao da doðem, jer sam...
- Hektore, jesi li dobro?

466
00:40:54,292 --> 00:40:57,458
