- Naravno.

473
00:41:11,783 --> 00:41:13,667
U redu?
- U redu.

474
00:41:14,375 --> 00:41:17,500
Nemoj da brineš.
Popuni formular, uzmi traku

475
00:41:17,700 --> 00:41:19,458
