476
00:41:19,658 --> 00:41:20,550
U redu.

477
00:41:20,750 --> 00:41:22,833
U redu, izvinite zbog toga...

478
00:41:22,875 --> 00:41:24,675
Možete li samo da...

479
00:41:24,875 --> 00:41:27,833
Potpišite u tom polju,
napišite svoje ime.

480
00:41:27,917 --> 00:41:31,375
