- Dobro jutro, Džimbo.

495
00:42:50,658 --> 00:42:53,250
Evo, sačuvali smo ti
tvoje staro mesto, gospodine.

496
00:42:53,450 --> 00:42:55,050
Izvinite.

497
00:42:55,250 --> 00:42:57,917
